    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1265577647216398336",
    "content": "<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年7月28日- </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2025年8月3日，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">规则预计于2025年8月4日生效，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">原规则链接：<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12</a> </span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">核心调整点：</span></span></span></strong></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">① \"虚假宣传\"场景调整：&ldquo;虚假宣传&rdquo;变更为&ldquo;发布违规宣传信息&rdquo;，并调整定义及处理措施；</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">② \"侵权违规\"场景调整：修订侵权违规的场景定义及对应处理措施；</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">③新增\"商品信息与实物不符\"、\"商品要素不一致\"、\"商品发布规避信息\"、\"冒用京东官方名义\"、\"不当使用关键词\"五个场景及对应处理措施。</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">修订后内容如下：</span></span></span></strong></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">1、调整：</span></span></span></strong></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">第三类 侵权违规</span></span></span></strong></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">3、侵权违规</span></span></strong>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">3.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">【违规定义】商家发布的商品或信息涉嫌不当使用他人商标权、著作权、专利权、肖像权以及其他类型权利，或者商家发布、传播或授意他人发布、传播不利于京东的网络信息、音视频等的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">3.1.1 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">不当使用他人商标权、著作权、专利权的行为：指包括不限于商家所出售的商品或发布的商品信息中、所使用的店铺名、域名中，存在不当使用他人商标权、著作权、专利权等权利的行为；或相关行为产生消费者投诉举报、负面舆情等不良后果。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.1.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">不当使用他人肖像权：指商家所发布的商品信息或出售的商品不当使用他人肖像权的行为。&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.1.3 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">知识产权投诉：指商家收到权利人发起的知识产权投诉，京东受理权利人所投诉的不当使用他人权利的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.1.4 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">发布影响京东名誉的信息：指商家发布、传播或授意他人发布、传播不利于京东的网络信息、音视频等的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.1.5 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">其他不当使用他人权利的行为：指商家其他不当使用他人权利的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【处理措施】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.2.1 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度轻微的，下架或删除违规商品，并限制创建商品及禁止上架待售商品7日。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">3.2.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度一般的，下架或删除违规商品，并限制创建商品及禁止上架待售商品7日，扣除违约金 100元-1000元不等。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">3.2.3 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度严重的，下架或删除违规商品，并限制创建商品及禁止上架待售商品（7日），扣除违约金2000元-10000元不等。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">3.2.4 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度极其严重的，下架或删除违规商品，并限制创建商品及禁止上架待售商品（30日），扣除违约金5000元-100000元不等。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">3.2.5 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">商家发布、传播或授意他人发布、传播不利于京东的网络信息、音视频等的，京东有权扣收不低于人民币1000000元的违约金；不足以弥补京东损失的部分，商家应继续予以赔偿。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.2.6 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">除上述措施外，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于扣除违约金、违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、禁止发布新商品、禁止上架待售商品、禁止投放或提报活动、禁止投放或播放广告、品牌停用和限制申请品牌、类目停用和限制开通类目、搜索降权、推荐降权、全店商品下架、降低店铺星级、屏蔽降权、账户止付、定额冻结、提高涉事店铺应交保证金金额、延长结算周期、执行店铺清退等处理措施，并且有权视商家违规影响，扣除商家部分或全部违规经营所得（订单款项），并对商家予以追责。</span></p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">第六类 信息违规 </span> </span></span></span></strong></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">16、【虚假宣传】调整为【发布违规宣传信息】：</span></span></span></strong></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">16.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">【违规情形】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">16.1.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">夸大或虚构功能功效：指商家在商品宣传中声称该商品具备某种特殊功效或特性，但实际商品并未包含相关功能、功效、资质或证明。或商家在商品描述、广告、营销活动或其他渠道中对商品的性能、效果或特点进行不实或过度夸张的宣传，导致消费者形成错误的预期，认为商品能够实现超出实际能力的功能或效果。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">16.1.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">使用广告法禁用词汇：指商家在商品的主图、标题、属性、商详等关键展示位置，使用被明确禁止的词汇或表述方式进行商品描述。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">16.1.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">虚假营销活动：指商家在商品宣传、广告或其他营销渠道中使用虚假、误导、夸大或过期的活动信息来吸引消费者参与营销活动，而实际情况与宣传内容不符，影响公平竞争和交易环境的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">16.1.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">虚假营销服务：指虚构根本不存在的服务或通过虚假、误导性、夸大或隐瞒关键信息的方式推广服务或在商品或服务的宣传中做出不切实际、无法实现或违背客观常识的服务承诺，误导消费者对商品或服务的期望的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">16.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">16.2.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度轻微：预警整改，整改失败/超期未整改下架违规商品；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">16.2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度一般：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品SKU过去30天成交金额的5%、最低100元，最高2000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">16.2.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品SKU过去30天成交金额的20%、最低500元，最高5000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">16.2.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度极其严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品SKU过去30天成交金额的50%及以上、最低5000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">16.2.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">2、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">新增：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21、【商品信息与实物不符】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">【违规情形】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.1.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">样式不符：指商家在商品的宣传中，提供的商品信息（如款式、颜色、图案、形状等）与实际商品存在明显差异的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.1.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">规格参数不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，提供与实际商品不符的规格或参数信息的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.1.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">材质不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，提供与实际商品材质不符的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.1.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">产地不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，商品产地与商品实际情况不符的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.1.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">品种不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，商品品种与商品实际情况不符的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.1.6</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">重量不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，提供与实际商品重量不符的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.1.7</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">虚拟商品与实际应用不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，提供商品实际应用与宣传不符的的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.1.8</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">滥用随机发货声明：指商家商品主图/标题/名称/详情页等位置标明&ldquo;随机发货&rdquo;字样，但存在以下误导/欺骗消费者行为：</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">1）随机发货信息展示不一致，即商品为随机发货商品，但商品主图/标题/名称/详情页等多位置展示为单一商品，误导消费者下单并引起消费者投诉，视为滥用随机发货声明信息；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">2）标注随机发货商品但实际非同款商品，即随机发货范围内商品品牌、功能、用途等发生明显变化，或因材质、构造变化而导致商品价值、质量发生变化，视为滥用随机发货声明范围。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3）随机发货页面发布规则详见：<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://psm.jd.com/article/articledetail.html?id=788\">https://psm.jd.com/article/articledetail.html?id=788</a></span> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.2.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度轻微：预警整改，整改失败/超期未整改下架违规商品；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度一般：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品SKU过去30天成交金额的5%、最低100元，最高2000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.2.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品SKU过去30天成交金额的20%、最低500元，最高5000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.2.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度极其严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品SKU过去30天成交金额的50%及以上、最低5000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">21.2.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">22、【商品要素不一致】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">22.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">【违规情形】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">22.1.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">属性不一致：<span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">指商品信息中出现的属性词，填写错误或在主图、商详、标题、销售属性、营销属性等位置描述不一致的情形</span>。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">22.1.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">销量不一致：指商品信息如标题、卖点、商详等位置的销量信息，与实际销量不一致的情形。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">22.1.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">其他商品要素不一致：指商品信息中除上述以外的其他要素不一致的情形。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">22.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">22.2.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度轻微：警告；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">22.2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度一般：预警整改，整改失败/超期未整改下架违规商品；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">22.2.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品SKU过去30天成交金额的5%、最低100元，最高2000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">22.2.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度极其严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品SKU过去30天成交金额的20%及以上、最低2000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">22.2.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23、【商品发布规避信息】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">【违规情形】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.1.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">更换商品：指商家在已有商品（SKU）链接上将原商品更换为另一款商品进行销售的行为，更换后的商品在类目、品牌、颜色、型号、品种等属性上发生了改变。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.1.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">图片利用视觉效果隐藏关键信息导致用户误解：指商家通过修改字体/图案大小、色彩等，导致从视觉上完全改变整体含义并产生消费者误解的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.2.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">更换商品：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.2.1.1</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度一般：扣除违约金500元；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.2.1.2</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度严重：扣除违约金2000元，违规商品下架；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.2.1.3</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度极其严重：扣除违约金5000元，违规商品下架；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.2.1.4</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.2.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">图片利用视觉效果隐藏关键信息导致用户误解：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.2.2.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度一般：警告；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.2.2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度严重：预警整改，超期未整改或整改失败下架违规商品；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.2.2.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度极其严重：下架违规商品、并扣除违约金最低500元；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">23.2.2.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">24、【冒用京东官方名义】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">24.1【违规定义】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">24.1.1</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">冒用京东官方名义：指商家推广商品过程中，未经平台同意，使用与京东平台相关的logo、图案、名称、活动等，以此来诱导或欺骗消费者进行点击或购买的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">24.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">24.2.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度轻微：警告；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">24.2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度一般：预警整改，整改失败/超期未整改下架违规商品；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">24.2.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品SKU过去30天成交金额的20%、最低500元，最高5000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">24.2.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度极其严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（根据严重程度而定，最低5000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">24.2.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25、【不当使用关键词】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.1【违规定义】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.1.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">关键词混淆：指商家在商品信息（标题、详情页、广告等）中，故意使用与商品无真实关联的热门关键词，通过误导性表述吸引流量或提升转化，但实际商品不具备关键词所描述的特征、授权或功能，属于违规营销行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.1.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">品牌词混淆：指在标题、宣传语、商品图片及商品详情等位置使用/滥用/堆砌其他品牌词（包括但不限于品牌的变形词或衍生词，如错别字、同音字、故意增加间隔符号等）来描述商品，与商品本身品牌不一致的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">关键词混淆：</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.1.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度轻微：警告；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.1.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度一般：预警整改，整改失败/超期未整改下架违规商品；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.1.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品SKU过去30天成交金额的20%、最低500元，最高5000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.1.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度极其严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（根据严重程度而定，最低5000元）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.1.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">品牌词混淆：</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.2.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度轻微：警告，违规商品下架；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度一般：违规商品下架、钱包冻结、扣除违约金1000-10000元不等（实际金额包括但不限于与商家经营收入、违规程度、违规影响等相关）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.2.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度严重：违规商品下架、钱包冻结、扣除违约金3000-30000元不等（实际金额包括但不限于与商家经营收入、违规程度、违规影响等相关）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.2.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">违规程度特别严重：违规商品下架、钱包冻结、扣除违约金5000-50000元不等（实际金额包括但不限于与商家经营收入、违规程度、违规影响等相关）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">25.2.2.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #fbeeb8;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次（两次及以上）或大量在售商品出现以上违规行为，或因上述行为引起重大投诉或舆情的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于限制创建商品、店铺商品搜索/推荐降权、禁止上架待售商品、永久限制通过接口批量操作商品、限制在售商品阈值、限制提报营销活动、属性屏蔽、店铺屏蔽、商品屏蔽、品牌停用、类目停用、冻结资金、页面止付、降低店铺星级、跨类目经营限制、店铺清退等处理措施。</span></span></p>\n</div>",
